# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Frontend Environment Variables — Local Development
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to ".env" and fill in your values.
# All variables are OPTIONAL.
#
# Without them the app works in "demo mode":
#   • Email OTP codes are printed to the browser console (F12 → Console)
#     instead of being sent by email — copy the code from there.
#   • Email verification links are also printed to the console.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── EmailJS (for OTP and password reset emails) ──────────────────────
# Sign up at https://www.emailjs.com to get these values.
# Leave empty to use demo mode (OTP shown in browser console).
VITE_EMAILJS_SERVICE_ID=
VITE_EMAILJS_PUBLIC_KEY=
VITE_EMAILJS_VERIFY_TEMPLATE=
VITE_EMAILJS_RESET_TEMPLATE=
